body:
I've done with functional tests.

To experiment this behavior, I made a odd topology which modifies ExclamationTopology to let spout emits 1000 tuples and sleeps 5 secs in nextTuple().
https://gist.github.com/HeartSaVioR/9ebac9f7f8503e878b0009a37c2b686b

I also turn off backpressure to not affect the test and also adjust receive buffer size and send buffer size to 16384.

> before patch
- complete latency

